{"tid":1156803,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"超級八達通","createTime":"2019-05-16T00:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T12:27:56.000Z","uid":66811,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"10ae70c44ffdb10acf63ae7082e49ff96a260364","tid":1156803,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:06:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190516/59600521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190516%2F59600521&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2Hfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=c572b5bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190516%2F59600521&h=83beb004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190516/59600521</a><br />\n<br />\n27歲失婚港姐何艷娟孔雀開屏，5月初才宣佈回復單身，跟坐擁30億身家的澳博營運總裁吳志誠閃離，結束了「壽命」不足1年的爺孫戀婚姻，一個華麗轉身，何艷娟被爆戀上已故教育家陳樹渠的長子陳燿璋，其家族資產逾200億，身家比何艷娟前夫更上一層樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢張超級八達通嘅搵錢速度，李嘉誠都甘拜下風"},{"pid":"90c5a1187c38e5b4501050839873a4592279f538","tid":1156803,"uid":99627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:31:26.000Z","msg":"呢張直頭係無credit limit既paywave喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63be6a72cffb9a83f24ab0f539986beade2e3cb6","tid":1156803,"uid":66811,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.tvmost.com.hk/most/uploads/images/2015/Article/2015.11/2015.11.24/ko/2(1).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tvmost.com.hk%2Fmost%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F2015%2FArticle%2F2015.11%2F2015.11.24%2Fko%2F2%281%29.jpg&h=d5dde221&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"308a4802f58f595e4c10de1c26cddb919d6355c6","tid":1156803,"uid":244624,"like":2,"dislike":1,"sc